w-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="162">You only need the <strong data-start="18" data-end="35">output tables</strong> for the <code data-start="44" data-end="52">tables</code> folder. Create them as separate files such as <strong data-start="99" data-end="112">Table1.md</strong> and <strong data-start="117" data-end="130">Table2.md</strong> or include them in your report.</p>
<h3 data-section-id="cvdwtx" data-start="164" data-end="236">Table 1: Comparison of CNN Models with and without Data Augmentation</h3>
